com.microsoft.azure.management.resources.fluentcore.collection

Interface SupportsBatchCreation<ResourceT extends Resource>

  • Type Parameters:
    ResourceT - the top level Azure resource type
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AvailabilitySets, BatchAccounts, LoadBalancers, NetworkInterfaces, Networks, NetworkSecurityGroups, PublicIpAddresses, RedisCaches, ResourceGroups, StorageAccounts, VirtualMachines, VirtualMachineScaleSets

    public interface SupportsBatchCreation<ResourceT extends Resource>
    Providing access to creating a batch of Azure top level resources of same type.

    (Note: this interface is not intended to be implemented by user code)

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods
